                            <comment id="14496600" author="thobbs" created="Wed, 15 Apr 2015 17:58:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Okay, I&apos;ll resolve this as a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9148&quot; title=&quot;Issue when modifying UDT&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-9148&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-9148&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14497976" author="blerer" created="Thu, 16 Apr 2015 12:01:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem was not fixed has part of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9148&quot; title=&quot;Issue when modifying UDT&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-9148&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-9148&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14497978" author="blerer" created="Thu, 16 Apr 2015 12:04:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After reviewing &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9148&quot; title=&quot;Issue when modifying UDT&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-9148&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-9148&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; I quickly made a patch for this issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch rely on the one of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9148&quot; title=&quot;Issue when modifying UDT&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-9148&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-9148&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for the tests so it should be applied after.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14505249" author="thobbs" created="Tue, 21 Apr 2015 16:47:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1, committed as &lt;tt&gt;aeadda5&lt;/tt&gt; with one additional unit test to cover nested tuples.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
